<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[الإِبْل]</span>: تخفيف الإِبِل.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ن]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[ابْنٌ]</span>: همزته غير أصلية، وليس هذا موضعه، وإِنما كتب ههنا للّفظ وهو من باب الباء والنون.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فِعْلة]</span> بالهاء<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[الإِبْرَة]</span>: معروفة.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وإِبرة الذراع:</span> مستدقُّها.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وإِبرة العقرب:</span> شوكتُها.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>... فَعَل، بالفتح<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[د]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[الأَبَد]</span>: الدهر،<span class="c5"> وجمعه:</span> آباد،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> خاالِدِينَ فِيهاا أَبَداً* <span class="c2">«١»</span>، <span class="c4">[و]</span> قال النابغة: <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>............... ... أَقْوَتْ وطَالَ عَلَيْهَا سَالِفُ الأَبَدِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[ق]</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[الأَبَق]</span>: القنَّب- ولم يأت في هذا الباب فاء- قال <span class="c2">«٣»</span>:<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>............... ... قَدْ أُحْكِمَتْ حَكَمَاتِ القِدِّ والأَبَقا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>و <span class="c4">[أَبَوٌ]</span>، <span class="c4">[الأبا]</span>: وجعٌ يأخذ المعزى والضأن<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
